xt-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Free Tool Shed's Pay Stub Generator creates professional pay stubs with earnings, deductions, and year-to-date totals — entirely in your browser. Supports hourly and salaried employees, multiple pay frequencies, custom tax rates, and instant PDF export. No sign-up, no upload, no recurring fee — a free alternative to PayStubCreator, Check Stub Maker, and FormPros.\"}]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Hourly & Salary Support\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Generate pay stubs for hourly employees with overtime or salaried workers with flat amounts. Supports bonus, commission, and tips.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Instant PDF Export\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Download professional pay stubs as PDF in one click. Your data never leaves your browser — everything is processed locally on your device.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Standard US Deductions\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"One-click setup for Federal, State, Social Security, Medicare, 401(k), and health insurance deductions. Add custom deductions too.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Year-to-Date Tracking\"}],[\"$\",\"p